{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-detail-tsx","path":"/detail/76d9a4d6-f261-568b-b220-84d833cbe045","result":{"pageContext":{"html":"<h1>概述</h1>\n<p><code>肖申克的救赎</code>，英文名为<code>The Shawshank Redemption</code> 。讲述的是一位年轻的银行家安迪·杜弗兰被指控杀害他的妻子与其情夫而入狱，本将在肖申克监狱中度过余生，但是在得知自己无罪后，越狱重获新生的故事。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 272px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/60c7bdce9a28145208127db624bb6922/76497/shawshank1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 88.51351351351352%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"info\"\n        title=\"info\"\n        src=\"/static/60c7bdce9a28145208127db624bb6922/76497/shawshank1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/60c7bdce9a28145208127db624bb6922/a80bd/shawshank1.jpg 148w,\n/static/60c7bdce9a28145208127db624bb6922/76497/shawshank1.jpg 272w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 272px) 100vw, 272px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>安迪本来是一个年轻有为的银行家，但被判了无期徒刑进入了肖申克监狱。一开始，他独来独往，不与人接触。后来在他们的一次的出公差，他通过帮队长海利报税节税，让监狱最严格的警长请了他的”同事们“每人三瓶啤酒，自此狱友们对他刮目相看。不得不说有文化就是不一样。典狱长也注意到了安迪的财经能力，将他调离了原来的洗衣房，协助布鲁克管理监狱图书馆，并要求安迪暗中帮他做账洗钱。同时，在此期间他不断写信给州议会，在他的努力下，州议会最终拨款修缮监狱图书馆。后来，他从名叫汤米的狱友的口中得知，当年的凶手另有其人而自己无罪。他想让典狱长帮助自己，不料典狱长将安迪关禁闭，并将汤米骗出监狱，令队长海利以逃狱为由将其枪杀。后来，在一次的惯例的早点名中，安迪不见了。他从自己挖了 17 年的地道中逃了出去，并在逃狱后用着洗钱时用的假身份—— “兰道·斯蒂文森”，取出了典狱长的很大一部分黑钱，并检举了典狱长。最终，典狱长畏罪自杀，安迪过上了自由的生活。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f18c9ad45e1a6841d73c4e6bde3a648a/8010b/shawshank2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"info\"\n        title=\"info\"\n        src=\"/static/f18c9ad45e1a6841d73c4e6bde3a648a/1c72d/shawshank2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f18c9ad45e1a6841d73c4e6bde3a648a/a80bd/shawshank2.jpg 148w,\n/static/f18c9ad45e1a6841d73c4e6bde3a648a/1c91a/shawshank2.jpg 295w,\n/static/f18c9ad45e1a6841d73c4e6bde3a648a/1c72d/shawshank2.jpg 590w,\n/static/f18c9ad45e1a6841d73c4e6bde3a648a/a8a14/shawshank2.jpg 885w,\n/static/f18c9ad45e1a6841d73c4e6bde3a648a/fbd2c/shawshank2.jpg 1180w,\n/static/f18c9ad45e1a6841d73c4e6bde3a648a/8010b/shawshank2.jpg 1455w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>几个细节</h1>\n<h2>安迪是布鲁克的第一个助手</h2>\n<p>安迪到图书馆的第一天就问布鲁克这些年有没有其他助手，布鲁克说没有自己的工作很轻松不需要助手。我们其实在这边就应该想到，典狱长将安迪调到图书馆，目的不是来帮助布鲁克，而是另有所图。不出所料，到图书馆的第一天，开始有狱警请求安迪财经方面的问题。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d700552504ed91af443d0f0259977dd6/3ce61/shawshank3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"info\"\n        title=\"info\"\n        src=\"/static/d700552504ed91af443d0f0259977dd6/1c72d/shawshank3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d700552504ed91af443d0f0259977dd6/a80bd/shawshank3.jpg 148w,\n/static/d700552504ed91af443d0f0259977dd6/1c91a/shawshank3.jpg 295w,\n/static/d700552504ed91af443d0f0259977dd6/1c72d/shawshank3.jpg 590w,\n/static/d700552504ed91af443d0f0259977dd6/a8a14/shawshank3.jpg 885w,\n/static/d700552504ed91af443d0f0259977dd6/fbd2c/shawshank3.jpg 1180w,\n/static/d700552504ed91af443d0f0259977dd6/3ce61/shawshank3.jpg 1227w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>瑞德说希望是危险的</h2>\n<p>瑞德在因用广播放音乐被关禁闭一个月后，朋友问他值吗，他说值，他在音乐中感受到了希望。瑞德告诉他希望是危险的，这也在后来的故事中得到了印证。汤米告诉了安迪事情的真相，给他带来了希望。但这样的希望给安迪带来了两个月的禁闭，给汤米带来了杀身之祸。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e49ab8f99ba33c1ab2f97ce88a146872/00d7d/shawshank4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.70270270270271%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"info\"\n        title=\"info\"\n        src=\"/static/e49ab8f99ba33c1ab2f97ce88a146872/1c72d/shawshank4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e49ab8f99ba33c1ab2f97ce88a146872/a80bd/shawshank4.jpg 148w,\n/static/e49ab8f99ba33c1ab2f97ce88a146872/1c91a/shawshank4.jpg 295w,\n/static/e49ab8f99ba33c1ab2f97ce88a146872/1c72d/shawshank4.jpg 590w,\n/static/e49ab8f99ba33c1ab2f97ce88a146872/a8a14/shawshank4.jpg 885w,\n/static/e49ab8f99ba33c1ab2f97ce88a146872/fbd2c/shawshank4.jpg 1180w,\n/static/e49ab8f99ba33c1ab2f97ce88a146872/00d7d/shawshank4.jpg 1218w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>故事中的主要人物</h1>\n<h2>安迪</h2>\n<p>作为故事的主要人物，他的故事确实十分传奇。先是入狱，再是给典狱长洗黑钱，后来逃狱了，还检举了典狱长。令他与肖申克监狱中的其他犯人不同的地方除了是他的学识，更在他的气质，他至始至终没有放弃过自由的追求。但他也并不像那个胖子狱友，第一天晚上就哭号，乞求出去，而被队长海利打死。他认为放音乐被关禁闭值得，他从音乐中感受到了希望，但众人却不敢奢望希望。这也正是他与众不同的地方。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3eae905353b4a6d14114e66125c3eab7/c293a/shawshank5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"info\"\n        title=\"info\"\n        src=\"/static/3eae905353b4a6d14114e66125c3eab7/1c72d/shawshank5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3eae905353b4a6d14114e66125c3eab7/a80bd/shawshank5.jpg 148w,\n/static/3eae905353b4a6d14114e66125c3eab7/1c91a/shawshank5.jpg 295w,\n/static/3eae905353b4a6d14114e66125c3eab7/1c72d/shawshank5.jpg 590w,\n/static/3eae905353b4a6d14114e66125c3eab7/a8a14/shawshank5.jpg 885w,\n/static/3eae905353b4a6d14114e66125c3eab7/fbd2c/shawshank5.jpg 1180w,\n/static/3eae905353b4a6d14114e66125c3eab7/c293a/shawshank5.jpg 1232w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>典狱长</h2>\n<p>这是这部电影中最具讽刺以为的一个角色。每个囚犯进入肖申克监狱前都会先见典狱长和狱警队长。而典狱长每次都会强调不允许亵渎上帝、圣经的重要性以及自己是一名虔诚的信徒。可是他却是这部电影中最黑的一个人。他让安迪帮我洗钱，甚至在知道安迪无罪的情况下，消灭安迪的人证，并威胁安迪，好让他继续为自己洗钱。最终，警员要来逮捕他时，他选择了畏罪自杀。他的办公室墙上的画极具讽刺意味————“主的审判迅速降临”。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a1e811a66f7d47ea3076338737447f46/c293a/shawshank7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"info\"\n        title=\"info\"\n        src=\"/static/a1e811a66f7d47ea3076338737447f46/1c72d/shawshank7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a1e811a66f7d47ea3076338737447f46/a80bd/shawshank7.jpg 148w,\n/static/a1e811a66f7d47ea3076338737447f46/1c91a/shawshank7.jpg 295w,\n/static/a1e811a66f7d47ea3076338737447f46/1c72d/shawshank7.jpg 590w,\n/static/a1e811a66f7d47ea3076338737447f46/a8a14/shawshank7.jpg 885w,\n/static/a1e811a66f7d47ea3076338737447f46/fbd2c/shawshank7.jpg 1180w,\n/static/a1e811a66f7d47ea3076338737447f46/c293a/shawshank7.jpg 1232w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>布鲁克</h2>\n<p>作为肖申克监狱的图书馆管理员，他已经被关了 50 年了，最后的成功假释却使他自杀，他是体制化的体制化的牺牲品。从一开始的惧怕监狱高墙，再到习惯高墙，最后是依赖于这堵高墙。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/41ce5e1853f07d11965db4b76d7e3688/d14c1/shawshank8.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"info\"\n        title=\"info\"\n        src=\"/static/41ce5e1853f07d11965db4b76d7e3688/1c72d/shawshank8.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/41ce5e1853f07d11965db4b76d7e3688/a80bd/shawshank8.jpg 148w,\n/static/41ce5e1853f07d11965db4b76d7e3688/1c91a/shawshank8.jpg 295w,\n/static/41ce5e1853f07d11965db4b76d7e3688/1c72d/shawshank8.jpg 590w,\n/static/41ce5e1853f07d11965db4b76d7e3688/a8a14/shawshank8.jpg 885w,\n/static/41ce5e1853f07d11965db4b76d7e3688/fbd2c/shawshank8.jpg 1180w,\n/static/41ce5e1853f07d11965db4b76d7e3688/d14c1/shawshank8.jpg 1234w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>瑞德</h2>\n<p>作为安迪在狱中的朋友，一开始他对安迪并不看好，不认为他能在狱中生存下去，认为他应该是菜鸟们中第一个崩溃的人。但安迪并没有崩溃，还在后来安迪和瑞德成为了挚友。瑞德就像是肖申克监狱的百货商店，没有他代购不到的东西，这也是安迪成功越狱的一大关键。他向我们阐述了一个很重要的概念——体制化。这也是布鲁克假释成功后自杀的原因，原本瑞德也会像布鲁克一样自杀。他在与社会隔绝了 40 年后，已经很难再适应这个社会了。但是他并没有，是安迪帮助他完成了对自己的救赎。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1b8303bb02531a1111361d838bd09d7b/1dae5/shawshank6.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"info\"\n        title=\"info\"\n        src=\"/static/1b8303bb02531a1111361d838bd09d7b/1c72d/shawshank6.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1b8303bb02531a1111361d838bd09d7b/a80bd/shawshank6.jpg 148w,\n/static/1b8303bb02531a1111361d838bd09d7b/1c91a/shawshank6.jpg 295w,\n/static/1b8303bb02531a1111361d838bd09d7b/1c72d/shawshank6.jpg 590w,\n/static/1b8303bb02531a1111361d838bd09d7b/a8a14/shawshank6.jpg 885w,\n/static/1b8303bb02531a1111361d838bd09d7b/fbd2c/shawshank6.jpg 1180w,\n/static/1b8303bb02531a1111361d838bd09d7b/1dae5/shawshank6.jpg 1229w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>汤米</h2>\n<p>作为一个给整个带来转折点的重要人物，汤米说出了真相，让自己领了盒饭。但他也是个上进的人，他主动找安迪请求他帮自己考学历证书，事实上他最后也成功了。也算是完成了对自己的救赎。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8ddc904d191b1e4444fffe1825dee9dd/902ab/shawshank9.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.70270270270271%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"info\"\n        title=\"info\"\n        src=\"/static/8ddc904d191b1e4444fffe1825dee9dd/1c72d/shawshank9.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8ddc904d191b1e4444fffe1825dee9dd/a80bd/shawshank9.jpg 148w,\n/static/8ddc904d191b1e4444fffe1825dee9dd/1c91a/shawshank9.jpg 295w,\n/static/8ddc904d191b1e4444fffe1825dee9dd/1c72d/shawshank9.jpg 590w,\n/static/8ddc904d191b1e4444fffe1825dee9dd/a8a14/shawshank9.jpg 885w,\n/static/8ddc904d191b1e4444fffe1825dee9dd/fbd2c/shawshank9.jpg 1180w,\n/static/8ddc904d191b1e4444fffe1825dee9dd/902ab/shawshank9.jpg 1204w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>总结</h1>\n<p><del>咕咕咕</del></p>","id":"76d9a4d6-f261-568b-b220-84d833cbe045","headings":[{"value":"概述","depth":1},{"value":"几个细节","depth":1},{"value":"安迪是布鲁克的第一个助手","depth":2},{"value":"瑞德说希望是危险的","depth":2},{"value":"故事中的主要人物","depth":1},{"value":"安迪","depth":2},{"value":"典狱长","depth":2},{"value":"布鲁克","depth":2},{"value":"瑞德","depth":2},{"value":"汤米","depth":2},{"value":"总结","depth":1}],"date":"Thursday, July 25, 2019 3:44 PM","tags":["随笔","影评"],"title":"肖申克的救赎"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}